{"type": "article", "id": 28734, "title": "BEAMS 与 Champion 的胶囊系列不错，以及，一大波男装秀发布 ｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-06-27T10:58:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 29333, "name": "男装秀"}, {"id": 3126, "name": "牛仔"}, {"id": 11718, "name": "印花"}, {"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 1124, "name": "巴黎"}, {"id": 5133, "name": "西班牙"}, {"id": 2831, "name": "中东"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 28551, "name": "Champion"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 9524, "name": "Kolor"}, {"id": 2040, "name": "KENZO"}, {"id": 10726, "name": "Dior Homme"}, {"id": 17255, "name": "KITH"}, {"id": 25545, "name": "Bleacher Report"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}, {"id": 16355, "name": "Acne"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 10632, "name": "UNDERCOVER"}, {"id": 15344, "name": "Mango"}, {"id": 18765, "name": "藤原浩"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702172821mtG3X8HR9jY2r7BJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/24/12024480/kylie-jenner-store-cosmetics\"><b>Kylie Jenner 要开实体美妆店</b></a>｜近日，与多个品牌推出过合作款彩妆的 Kylie Jenner 在 Snapchat 账号上宣布，即将开一家自己的实体美妆店 Kylie Cosmetic，她目前正在寻找店面。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/undercover-furniture-linehttp://hypebeast.com/2016/6/undercover-furniture-line\"><b>UNDERCOVER 将推出家具产品</b></a>｜服装品牌 UNDERCOVER 由日本设计师高桥盾创立，近日他在 Instagram 上宣布将与设计师 Kazuya Sasaki 合作推出家具产品，后者所在的 Small Clone 曾为 UNDERCOVER 和 White Mountaineering 负责门店设计。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionmag.com/news/Isabel-Marant-confirms-exclusive-negotiations-with-Montefiore-Investment,707401.html\"><b>法国投资公司收购 Isabel Marant  51% 股份</b></a>｜法国品牌 Isabel Marant  近日宣布，法国投资公司 Montefiore Investment 收购其 51% 股份，成为合作伙伴，帮助品牌在全球扩张以及巩固数字渠道。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Mango-to-open-4-megastores-in-Saudi-Arabia-and-the-Philippines,707334.html\">Mango 在菲律宾及沙特阿拉伯开 4 家卖场店</a></b>｜西班牙时装品牌 Mango 继续在中东和亚洲扩张，宣布在菲律宾和沙特阿拉伯新开 4 间大卖场店，面积都在 600-800 平方米。沙特阿拉伯是 Mango 在中东最大的市场，也是全世界第六大，从 1988 年进入这一地区以来，已经开了 60 家门店以及 2 家卖场店。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">日本百货 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/the-daily-street-beams-champion-capsule-collection-editorial\">BEAMS 与运动品牌 Champion 合作的胶囊系列</a>释出，皆为日常的街头穿着：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172754rlnvgUIRc7qhW31j.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172754dlkQqHh0bv7C1uA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172754lKg7TzeFvuAM5kYh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021727551Jrifthapm6lLWnu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172755FhBAofqS3QUYJzem.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021727568kmGCrRKh0xw6Jia.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>藤原浩的品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/fragment-design-louis-vuitton-collection\"> Fragment 与 Louis Vuitton 合作系列</a>发布：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172756nwQrN4A56GvXYxy9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172757pX8ufEIcVYMALTn7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172757cIyf2eNUvVY5QrEL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172758XJPF6dV42DjI7fEo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172758iefWz0k4XJuyMIhB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172759modHC3B2S6lGEfWg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172759TvZ5pGOPB3NK20bh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/dior-homme-spring-summer-17\">Dior Homme 把 2017 春夏大秀搬到了巴黎网球俱乐部</a>，现场装扮成了游乐场的样子：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172759DNoPlXYJGyIkcxQU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172800zFSZHsGieQLj8cIv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172800bJOcuZ3B8P9KnA4i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172801RyKfUEC5b0uYdSsx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172802qmAjo4B3GhF06f9i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/u